sequenceDiagram
    actor S as Student
    participant FE as Frontend React
    participant MW as Auth Middleware
    participant TC as Test Controller
    participant DB as MongoDB
    S->>FE: Select Job Role for Test
    FE->>MW: GET /api/v1/test/role JWT
    MW->>MW: Verify JWT
    MW->>TC: Forward Request
    TC->>DB: RoleTest.findOne role
    DB-->>TC: MCQ Questions
    TC-->>FE: Questions without correct answers
    FE-->>S: Display Test Page OMR Style
    S->>FE: Submit Answers
    FE->>MW: POST /api/v1/test/submit JWT + Answers
    MW->>TC: Forward Request
    TC->>DB: Fetch Correct Answers
    TC->>TC: Calculate Score and Knowledge Level
    TC->>TC: Compute Career Readiness Score
    TC->>DB: TestResult.create score level readiness
    DB-->>TC: Saved
    TC-->>FE: JSON score knowledgeLevel careerReadiness
    FE-->>S: Display Test Result Page
